{
  "chapter": "045",
  "title": "韩世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩</span>的祖先与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>同姓，都姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬氏</span>。其后有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国，受封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">韩原</span>，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩武子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩武子\">武子（韩武子）</span>之后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三世（时长）</span>出了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>，从封地为姓，是为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩氏</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋景公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>时的人。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司寇</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屠岸贾</span>将要作乱，要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋灵公\">灵公（晋灵公）</span>的贼人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵盾</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵盾</span>已经死了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屠岸贾</span>还想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀他的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵朔</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>劝阻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：屠岸贾\">贾（屠岸贾）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：屠岸贾\">贾（屠岸贾）</span>不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩厥\">厥（韩厥）</span>便告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵朔</span>让他逃亡。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵朔\">朔（赵朔）</span>说：\"你若能使<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>氏的祭祀不绝，我死了也无憾。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>答应了他。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：屠岸贾\">贾（屠岸贾）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩厥\">厥（韩厥）</span>称病不出。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程婴</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙杵臼</span>藏匿<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>氏孤儿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵武</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩厥\">厥（韩厥）</span>是知情的。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋景公\">景公（晋景公）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩厥\">厥（韩厥）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郤克</span>率兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百乘</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鞍</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐顷公</span>，俘<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">获</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">逢丑父</span>。这时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>设<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六卿</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>居于一卿之位，号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩献子\">献子（韩献子）</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋景公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十七年</span>，生病，占卜得知是先祖大业未成的人作祟。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>便称述<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵成季</span>的功劳，如今其后人无人主祭，以此感动<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋景公\">景公（晋景公）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：晋景公\">景公（晋景公）</span>问道：\"还有后代吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩厥\">厥（韩厥）</span>于是说出<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵武</span>，景公便归还<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>原有的田邑，让<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>的祭祀得以延续。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋悼公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩献子</span>告老。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩献子\">献子（韩献子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣子\">宣子（韩宣子）</span>代立。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣子\">宣子（韩宣子）</span>迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">州</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋平公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴季札</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国的政权最终要归于<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋顷公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩宣子</span>与<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏</span>共同瓜分<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">祁氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">羊舌氏</span>的十个县。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋定公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣子\">宣子（韩宣子）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵简子</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">范</span>氏、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">中行氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣子\">宣子（韩宣子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩贞子\">贞子（韩贞子）</span>代立。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩贞子\">贞子（韩贞子）</span>迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩贞子\">贞子（韩贞子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩简子\">简子（韩简子）</span>代立。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩简子\">简子（韩简子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩庄子\">庄子（韩庄子）</span>代立。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩庄子\">庄子（韩庄子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩康子\">康子（韩康子）</span>代立。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩康子\">康子（韩康子）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵襄子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏桓子</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：荀瑶\">知伯（荀瑶）</span>，瓜分他的土地，土地日益扩大，大于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩康子\">康子（韩康子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩武子\">武子（韩武子）</span>代立。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩武子\">武子（韩武子）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了郑国的国君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郑幽公\">幽公（郑幽公）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩武子\">武子（韩武子）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩景侯\">景侯（韩景侯）</span>继位。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩景侯\">景侯（韩景侯）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩景侯\">虔（韩景侯）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍丘</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">负黍</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，韩与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>都被列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳翟</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩景侯\">景侯（韩景侯）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩列侯\">列侯（韩列侯）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩列侯\">取（韩列侯）</span>继位。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩列侯\">列侯（韩列侯）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">聂政</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侠累</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六邑</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩列侯\">列侯（韩列侯）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩文侯\">文侯（韩文侯）</span>继位。这一年<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏文侯</span>去世。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩文侯\">文侯（韩文侯）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">执</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宋君</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桑丘</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">反</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灵丘</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩文侯\">文侯（韩文侯）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩哀侯\">哀侯（韩哀侯）</span>继位。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩哀侯\">哀侯（韩哀侯）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>瓜分<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，因而迁都到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩严</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>他的国君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩哀侯\">哀侯（韩哀侯）</span>。他的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩懿侯\">懿侯（韩懿侯）</span>继位。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩懿侯\">懿侯（韩懿侯）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马陵</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏惠王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宅阳</span>会盟。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">澮</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩懿侯\">懿侯（韩懿侯）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span>继位。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西山</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄池</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">硃</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东周</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陵观</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邢丘</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申不害</span>任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，修习法<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">术</span>、推行治道，国内得以治理，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>不来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩姬</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>他的国君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span>前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申不害</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，大旱，却建造<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">高门</span>（高大的城门）。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屈宜臼</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span>不会走出这座门。为什么？因为时机不对。我所谓时机，不是说时日，而是说人本来有利时与不利时。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span>曾经有利的时候，没有建高门。去年<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>，今年旱灾，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span>不在此时体恤民之急需，反而更加奢侈，这就叫'时事艰难而举止奢张'。\" <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">高门</span>建成，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩昭侯\">昭侯（韩昭侯）</span>去世，果然没能出这座门。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣惠王\">宣惠王（韩宣惠王）</span>继位。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣惠王\">宣惠王（韩宣惠王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军的将领<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩举</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，君号改为王。与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">区鼠</span>会盟。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>我，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">脩鱼</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浊泽</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span>获<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宧\">宧（韩宧）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申差</span>。 <span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩氏</span>情势危急，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>说：\"盟国不可依靠。现在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>已经很久了，王不如借<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>讲和，拿一座名城送给秦国，备好<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>兵，和秦一起南<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，这是一失换两得的计策。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>说：\"好。\" 于是准备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>出行，将要西去向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>求和。 <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>听说后大为恐慌，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈轸</span>告诉他这事。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈轸</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>已经很久了，如今又得到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的一座名城、齐全的兵<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>合兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，这是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>祝祷求之的事。如今已经得到了，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国必定被伐。请大王听我的，为此在国境四境内戒严，发兵号称救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，让<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">战车</span>满道路，派可信的使者，多带<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，厚携礼币，使韩相信王确实救他。就算<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>不听我们的，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>必定感激王，不会列雁阵来进攻，这样<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>就不和了，秦兵虽至，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>也不会遭大祸。若能让韩听从我们绝和于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>必大怒，深深怨恨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>南交<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，必轻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>；轻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，对付<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>便不恭敬：这样就凭借<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>之兵而免除<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的祸患。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>说：\"好。\" 于是四境戒严，兴师号称救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。 <span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">战车</span>满道路，派可信的使者，多带<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，厚携礼币。 使者对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>说：\"寡人之国虽小，已全部发兵了。愿大国纵情对付<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，寡人愿以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>殉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>听后大悦，便中止了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>的出行。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>说：\"不可。真正<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>我们的是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，以虚名救我们的是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。王靠<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的虚名，而轻率地与强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>绝交，王必为天下大笑。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>并非<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>之国，又不是平素约定共同谋<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的国家。秦已有伐韩之势，楚才发兵号称救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，这必是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈轸</span>的计谋。况且王已派人向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>通报了，如今不去，这是欺骗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。轻率欺骗强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>而相信<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的谋臣，恐怕王必定要后悔。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>不听，终于与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>绝交。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>因此大怒，增加<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，大战，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的援军不到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>，秦大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>我军于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岸门</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子仓</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>做人质以求和。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，韩与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屈丐</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丹阳</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八万</span>。 这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣惠王\">宣惠王（韩宣惠王）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子仓</span>继位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩襄王\">襄王（韩襄王）</span>。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩襄王\">襄王（韩襄王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦武王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临晋</span>会盟。 那年秋天，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六万</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦武王</span>去世。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>又把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>归还我国。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子婴</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>后归来。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>我，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穰</span>。 又与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐眛</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子婴</span>去世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子咎</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子虮虱</span>争做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虮虱</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>做人质。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子咎\">咎（公子咎）</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虮虱</span>逃亡在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>很想送他<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">内</span>（回韩）。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方城</span>之外，您何不让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍氏</span>旁筑万户之都，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>必然发兵救之，您一定会做将军。您就趁机用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的军队奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虮虱</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">内</span>（送入韩国），他一定听您的，也必定以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>的地方封您。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子咎\">咎（公子咎）</span>听从了他的计谋。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍氏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>求救。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>还未发兵，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙昧</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>说：\"您以为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙昧</span>答道：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">秦王</span>说：'请借道<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郑</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span>，出兵<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>境以等候您'，大概不会符合我们的期望。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>说：\"您以为真会这样吗？\" 答道：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">秦王</span>必定承袭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>的旧智。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁</span>的时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">秦王</span>说：'与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>屈折便归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>本来就是楚的盟国，这样<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>就孤立了。不如出兵使之受挫，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>大战，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>便可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>之外而归。'如今秦表面上说与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>合作，其实暗中亲善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。您等着<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>出兵受挫，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>一到必定轻易与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>战。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>暗中知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>没真打算用兵，必定很容易和您对峙。您作战若<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，便与您一起乘胜追击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，延及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三川</span>而归。您作战若不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>封锁<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三川</span>据守，您就没法救了。我私下为您担忧。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马庚\">庚（司马庚）</span>三次往返于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭鱼</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">商於</span>相会，他们说的是收回印玺，其实像是有盟约。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>恐惧，说：\"这样怎么办？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙昧</span>说：\"您一定要先顾<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>而后考虑<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，先顾自身而后考虑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>。您不如赶紧让国家与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>联合，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>必将委国于您。您所厌恶的是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>，而其实并不是要丢弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>解<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍氏</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>又对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦太后</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">琇戎</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公叔伯婴</span>担心<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">内</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虮虱</span>（送他入韩），您何不为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>求<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">质子</span>？<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚王</span>若答应<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">入</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">质子</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公叔伯婴</span>便知<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>不把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虮虱</span>当回事，必定使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>联合。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>挟持<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>来困<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏氏</span>不敢与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>联合，这样<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>就孤立了。您又可替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>求<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">质子</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>若不答应，便与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>结怨。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>挟持<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>必定看重您。您挟着<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的重量来积德于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公叔伯婴</span>必以国事等候您。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">虮虱</span>终究没能回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公子咎\">咎（公子咎）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王来朝。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">函谷</span>驻军。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>给了我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河外</span>及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩襄王\">襄王（韩襄王）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子咎</span>继位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩釐王\">釐王（韩釐王）</span>。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩釐王\">釐王（韩釐王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙喜</span>率<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊阙</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十四万</span>，俘<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙喜\">喜（公孙喜）</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百里</span>给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夏山</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>我军。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西周</span>会盟，辅佐<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">出</span>亡。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在两<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>之间会盟。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：暴鸢\">暴烝（暴鸢）</span>去救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：暴鸢\">烝（暴鸢）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">开封</span>。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>告急，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>不救。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">韩相国（韩信）</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈筮</span>说：\"情势急迫，希望您虽然有病，为韩国走一趟。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈筮</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span>说：\"情势急吗？所以派您来。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈筮</span>说：\"并不急。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span>大怒，说：\"这像是能够替您的君主出使吗？使者冠盖相望地告诉我们敝邑情势危急，您来却说不急，为何？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈筮</span>说：\"那<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>若急便将改变立场投靠他国，正因为不急，我才又来。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穰侯</span>说：\"您不用见秦王，请我现在就发兵救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。\" <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">八天（时长）</span>就到了，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span>之下击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩釐王\">釐王（韩釐王）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩桓惠王\">桓惠王（韩桓惠王）</span>继位。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩桓惠王\">桓惠王（韩桓惠王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陉</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汾</span>旁<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">城</span>（筑城）。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太行</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>我军，我<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上党郡守</span>带<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党郡</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">马服子</span>的士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀万</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">负黍</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>去世。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城皋</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>全部<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>。 <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十三城</span>。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩桓惠王\">桓惠王（韩桓惠王）</span>去世，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安\">王安（韩安）</span>继位。"
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安\">王安（韩安）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>危急，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>扣留<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>，之后<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他。"
    },
    "34": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安\">王安（韩安）</span>，尽占其地，设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍州郡</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国于是灭亡。"
    },
    "35": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩厥</span>以其言感动<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋景公</span>，使<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>氏孤儿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵武\">武（赵武）</span>得以承续，以成就<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程婴</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙杵臼</span>之义，这是天下的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">阴德</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩氏</span>之功，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国时还看不出有何特大之处。然而他们与<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏</span>最终成为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，历<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多代（时长）</span>，这大概是应当的啊！"
    },
    "36": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩氏</span>的祖先，其实是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周武王\">武（周武王）</span>的宗亲。 事奉微小之国，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>中没有记载。 后代事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国，居处于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">韩原</span>。 <span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>氏孤儿得立，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：荀瑶\">智伯（荀瑶）</span>可取而代之。 既迁徙到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>，又<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">负黍</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩景侯\">景（韩景侯）</span>与<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵</span>同为诸侯，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩宣惠王\">惠（韩宣惠王）</span>又僭称为王。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">脩鱼</span>击<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>韩，韩与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>会于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">区鼠</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>虽出使秦国，也止不住<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狼虎</span>（秦国）之势。"
    }
  }
}